lead_paragraph: Nearly three months after the election, Michael Huffington today finally withdrew his challenge to Senator Dianne Feinstein of California. Mr. Huffington, a former Republican representative from California's 22d Congressional District, which includes most of Santa Barbara, congratulated the Democratic incumbent on her narrow victory last Nov. 8 in the nation's most expensive Senate race.

headline.main: Challenge in California Senate Race Is Withdrawn
